  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Looking for a Roguelike Strategy Auto Battler? You're in the right place!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/c5f5be6619cb35274ffc38ea75f8f2c0.poster.avif?t=1730797191\" width=622 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/c5f5be6619cb35274ffc38ea75f8f2c0.webm?t=1730797191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/c5f5be6619cb35274ffc38ea75f8f2c0.mp4?t=1730797191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself as a commander in this tactical game, where you must choose the right units to defeat enemy forces. Experiment with different unit combinations as you lead the armies of the <strong>Kingdom</strong>, <strong>Greenskins</strong>, <strong>Undead</strong>, or <strong>Barbarians</strong>. Select your Commander and guide your troops through a randomly generated map, culminating in a final clash with the BOSS! Is your army strong enough to defeat him?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/6b3b7ee58b5bdf5aee5d58c22bcc655b.poster.avif?t=1730797191\" width=622 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/6b3b7ee58b5bdf5aee5d58c22bcc655b.webm?t=1730797191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/6b3b7ee58b5bdf5aee5d58c22bcc655b.mp4?t=1730797191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you prefer a more classic approach to strategy and tactics, test your skills in over <strong>100 challenging missions</strong>! Use your resources wisely to triumph in increasingly difficult battles!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Looking for a Roguelike Strategy Auto Battler? You're in the right place!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/c5f5be6619cb35274ffc38ea75f8f2c0.poster.avif?t=1730797191\" width=622 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/c5f5be6619cb35274ffc38ea75f8f2c0.webm?t=1730797191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/c5f5be6619cb35274ffc38ea75f8f2c0.mp4?t=1730797191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenge yourself as a commander in this tactical game, where you must choose the right units to defeat enemy forces. Experiment with different unit combinations as you lead the armies of the <strong>Kingdom</strong>, <strong>Greenskins</strong>, <strong>Undead</strong>, or <strong>Barbarians</strong>. Select your Commander and guide your troops through a randomly generated map, culminating in a final clash with the BOSS! Is your army strong enough to defeat him?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/6b3b7ee58b5bdf5aee5d58c22bcc655b.poster.avif?t=1730797191\" width=622 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/6b3b7ee58b5bdf5aee5d58c22bcc655b.webm?t=1730797191\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2594290/extras/6b3b7ee58b5bdf5aee5d58c22bcc655b.mp4?t=1730797191\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you prefer a more classic approach to strategy and tactics, test your skills in over <strong>100 challenging missions</strong>! Use your resources wisely to triumph in increasingly difficult battles!</p>",
